Text:

Text:

Text:

Text:

Text:

Name: t_personal
Text:
OH HELL YEEEAAAH!

Name: t_personal
Text:

Text:

Text:

Text:

Text:

Text:

Text:

Text:

Yeah, never mind. I don't think I wanna hear about all that.

Name: t_personal
Text:
Well, anyway, we won, so...
Thanks, bud!

Name: t_temp
Text:
Extremely charismatic, and able to say pretty much
anything and be forgiven, affording him great Stealth ability.
When faking a role, he goes all in and is quickly found out.
